Track More Marketing Cloud Personalization Product Metrics

Use the Consumption report to proactively manage org-wide total and dataset-specific usage of both monthly unique visitors and named individual profile limits.

Where: This change applies to all Marketing Cloud Personalization editions.

How: From the Marketing Cloud Personalization main navigation menu, hover over Reports and select Usage | Personalization Consumption Report.
